{ Starting immediate attack. This is an improvement over the @@StartBracket@@still very good@@EndBracket@@ move  16...Bf5  that was played in the model game,Grischuk-Aronian, the first important game in the 6...Nf6 and 7...Nh5 variation and one that perfectly demonstrated Black's dynamic potential. Please take a look to see how Black wins these positions. }
