15. Nd6 { This prevents ...b5, which would follow after  15.Ne5  b5 } 15... Qb6
{ Now the knight is hanging. } 16. Ne4 Qa5
{ After a nice triangulation of the queen @@StartBracket@@a6-b6-a5@@EndBracket@@ and return to a5, Black threatens ...b5 and ...Rc8 with a strong initiative. }
