22. Be5 { The immediate   22.Nd6?  is bad in view of  22...b5 } 22... Ra8
{ Planning ...Qa6. } 23. Bd6
{ Now that Black doesn't have the ...b5 motif @@StartBracket@@as in the line after the immediate 22. Bd6@@EndBracket@@ White comes back to the plan of exchange of the bishops. }
