5. e3 O-O 6. Bd3 { This allows Black to win a tempo by taking on c4. } 6...
dxc4 7. Bxc4 a6
{ Black wants to expand with ... b5, which would allow for the development of the bishop to b7. Then he will follow up with ... c5 and ...Nbd7 with very harmonious development. }
