1. d4 d5 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Be7 4. Nf3 Nf6
{ Now White has 3 alternative moves to the main lines. These are 5.g3, 5.e3 and 5.Qc2. }
5. Qc2
{ White wants to transpose to the Exchange Variation but with the queen on c2 preventing the development of the bishop on f5. }
5... c5
{ The most direct way, trying to take over the initiative immediately. With his last move, White weakened control over d4 so Black takes immediate advantage. Another idea of White's 5. Qc2 is to move-order Black out of the intended repertoire in case of   5...O-O  6.Bg5  h6  7.Bxf6  Bxf6  as here Black has ...O-O instead of the preferred ...dxc4. }
6. cxd5 cxd4 { An intermediate move attacking the c3-knight. } 7. Qa4+
{ With this check, White goes after the pawn, but he concedes the initiative to Black. }
7... Bd7 8. Qxd4 exd5
{ Black sacrifices a pawn for the initiative. The compensation consists of his quick development @@StartBracket@@and White's lag in it@@EndBracket@@ and the initiative thanks to his more active pieces. }
9. Nxd5 Qa5+ { Forcing the knight to retreat. } 10. Nc3 Nc6
{ Black has good compensation here thanks to his lead in development. White needs to waste time moving his already developed pieces, first it was the queen's knight and now it is the queen. }
11. Qd1 O-O { Black finishes development. } 12. e3 Rad8
{ Centralizing the rook. } 13. Bd2 Qh5
{ The queen is transferred to the kingside. After } 14. Be2 Qg6
{ Black's idea is to attack the vulnerable pawn on g2. } 15. O-O Bh3
{ Forcing the knight to e1 and opening the d-file for the doubling of the rooks. }
16. Ne1 Rd7 17. Kh1 Rfd8 { Black's activity is quite threatening. } 18. gxh3
Rxd2 19. Qb1
{ White must seek exchange of queens as the black queen can become very dangerous after ...Qf5, attacking the pawn on h3. }
19... Nd5 { Attacking the knight that defends the bishop on e2. } 20. Qxg6 hxg6
21. Nxd5 R8xd5
{ Since the bishop on e2 and the pawn on b2 are attacked, Black regains the pawn after... }
22. Bf3 Ra5
{ When his activity and better pawn structure give him the slightly better endgame. }
