8. Nxc6 Nxc6
{ He has successfully solved the development problems and all his pieces are active, exerting pressure on White's center. }
9. O-O O-O
{ Black is fully developed now and White needs to solve the issue with the hanging pawn on d4. }
10. d5
{ This is a direct attempt to solve the problem of the defence of the pawn on d4, but since Black is better developed this opening of the game suits him fine. }
10... exd5 11. Nxd5 Nxd5
